0:
”Alexa, ask Bruin Swiper where I should eat”
”Alexa, ask Bruin Swiper where to eat”
”Alexa, ask Bruin Swiper what dining hall to eat at”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: bruin swiper
des: Ever been stuck trying to figure out where to eat? Bruin Swiper can help! Just ask Bruin Swiper where you should eat, and it will automatically get a list of currently open UCLA dining halls and suggest one to you! It's as simple as that!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
